    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Oh, yes, agreed.\n\nBut my point was more about the `Stats` widget and any widget with a generic name. I assume that if we have users building their website with React, they might already have a `Stats` widget on their side which will collide with our own.\n",
